author: Jean Russell
text: So sorry to hear that Dean Stockwell has passed.  I have watched him since the beginning of his career.  We sort of grew up together.  He was a beautiful child and an extremely talented actor.  He will be sorely missed.

author: Jean Russell
text: I am happy to see the brothers United for this magnificent occasion.  I hope that this will bring them together again and realize how painful it would be for their mother to see them estranged.  William and Harry come together for Diana and each other.
